title: One Less Reason [fixed]
description:
sorry guys and gals the files for the last torrent for some reason got corrupted and kept giving me errors at 98% so i made a new one of the exact files.

Here is the entire One Less Reason Discography including the latest release
and some extra tracks that were taken from the Myspace page. the extra tracks are covers and acoustics. 
   This band kicks ass. they are originally from Jackson, Tennessee which is about 50 miles from me. They were called Lapdog before changing their name to O.L.R. they are very particular about their music. they had a record deal at one time but had issues with the producing of the music. so they are indie last i knew. they write, record, and produce their own stuff and from the sounds of it they know what they are doing. They play alot of concerts and return to Jackson Tenn very often. 

If you havent heard them take a listen....
SUPPORT THE ARTISTS...BUY THE MUSIC IF YOU LIKE IT. 
google the band and you can find the cd&#039;s for sale.
help support a really great band....

Files arent packed so if you already have some of their stuff you can just get what you need.
